    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "If the user has their own preferences for an interactive prompt, then they can set PYTHONSTARTUP in their bashrc. If a program depends on character-for-character output of the interactive prompt, then it should either set the -E option or set PYTHONSTARTUP to \"\".\n"
